Name: MoonRun
About the game: MoonRun is a retro action-shooter set on the surface of a desolate moon in outer space. Traverse your battle hardend truck on an intense mission off-world, to conquer the invading forces behest on stealing your valuable resources. Get locked and stocked with an assortment of weapons, helping you blow the enemy scum right out of the sky . Get rewarded handsomely for doing so and really put your skills to the test in taking down the vile mastermind behind this senseless droid invasion.
